title: Give Birth To Your Dreams | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Give Birth To Your Dreams | Joel Osteen
description:
God’s promises are like seeds planted in our hearts. If God gave you the dream, it’s only a matter of time before you see it come to pass. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
